{"tid":1071710,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都比佢呃左？","createTime":"2019-03-21T13:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T18:04:00.000Z","uid":125813,"like":16,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"caf5c04ce9ade2643ee6863857c943f200a6066c","tid":1071710,"uid":125813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T13:57:49.000Z","msg":"見到係冇名，已經即刻狗衝<br />\n睇個盒以為係成座咁買，仲要見到29蚊only，即刻諗都無諗！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GW0HsMA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGW0HsMA.png&h=d79806c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知返到去見到原來得咁少嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tAPJcdg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtAPJcdg.png&h=521615a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得條樓梯，一隻冇名同張床，比佢打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲話有100期，買曬成座就要10k了。。好彩而家首期都只係29蚊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tf89Sdh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftf89Sdh.png&h=6456e695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人都做左苦主？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663e9e13137c68d82926343f144dba36da8dd19e","tid":1071710,"uid":101253,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T13:59:15.000Z","msg":"咁都叫做苦主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397bb99be99bb9ef1d6e6b41182450dca4f5b62a","tid":1071710,"uid":115441,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"之後唔買其實都ok<br />\n單第一期你咪當扭左個蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9338a54e12375853a088d789fcec61bc24dd9e","tid":1071710,"uid":84102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:02:42.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec2513ab1d034314c445a049b0c703bc5f2eedf","tid":1071710,"uid":188493,"lik